trans-unit.source: Defines several XPath functions and namespace mappings commonly used when evaluating XPath expressions against SOAP documents.
trans-unit.target: Definerer flere XPath-funksjoner og navneområdet tilordninger brukes vanligvis under evaluering av XPath-uttrykk mot SOAP-dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: The XPath engine has full XPath context support and uses the .NET Framework's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext> class in the same way that <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> does to implement this support.
trans-unit.target: XPath-motoren er full XPath konteksten støtte og bruker .NET Framework <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>klassen i samme måte som <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>finnes å implementere denne støtten.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext> is an abstract class that allows developers to implement custom XPath function libraries and declare XPath variables.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>er en abstrakt klasse som gjør det mulig for utviklere å implementere egendefinerte XPath-funksjonen biblioteker og deklarere XPath variabler.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext> is an <xref:System.Xml.XmlNamespaceManager> and thus also contains the namespace prefix mappings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>er en <xref:System.Xml.XmlNamespaceManager>og dermed også inneholder navneområdeprefikset tilordningene.</xref:System.Xml.XmlNamespaceManager></xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>

trans-unit.source: The filter engine implements an <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext> named XPathMessageContext.
trans-unit.target: Motoren for filter implementerer en <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>navnet XPathMessageContext.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XsltContext>

trans-unit.source: XPathMessageContext defines custom functions that can be used in XPath expressions and it declares several common namespace prefix mappings.
trans-unit.target: XPathMessageContext definerer egendefinerte funksjoner som kan brukes i XPath-uttrykk og den angir flere vanlige navneområdeprefikset tilordninger.

trans-unit.source: Several classes including this one, <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>, and <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> use the <xref:System.Xml.NameTable> class internally to store attribute and element names.
trans-unit.target: Flere klasser som er inkludert dette <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>, og <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>Bruk av <xref:System.Xml.NameTable>klassen internt til å lagre navn for attributt- og elementverdier.</xref:System.Xml.NameTable> </xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>

trans-unit.source: When an element or attribute name occurs multiple times in an XML document, it is stored only once in the <xref:System.Xml.NameTable>.
trans-unit.target: Når et navn for elementet eller attributtet vises flere ganger i et XML-dokument, lagres den bare én gang i <xref:System.Xml.NameTable>.</xref:System.Xml.NameTable>

trans-unit.source: The names are stored as common language runtime (CLR) object types.
trans-unit.target: Navnet som er lagret som common language runtime (CLR) objekttyper.

trans-unit.source: This enables you to do object comparisons on these strings rather than a more expensive string comparison.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du kan objekt sammenligninger i disse strenger i stedet for en mer kostbar strengsammenligning.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Xml.NameTable> class used internally to store strings.
